# Compose false-green

Do not run `docker compose`, `smoke-test*.sh`, `integration-smoke.sh`, `adversarial.sh`,
or other stack/smoke scripts from worktree cwd (including `cd` to main root then smoke).
Parent runs merge verification on main repo root. See `docs/harness/false-green-checklist.md`.
